<p><span style="color: rgb(98, 142, 124); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255);">2月7日，江软经济管理学院召开全院大会，全体教职工参加，其中一项是关于师德师风建设。借此大会，经济管理学院筑牢师德师风之基，以小流汇冮之势，守望教育初心。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(98, 142, 124); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240306/1709686365238094171.jpg" title="1709686365238094171.jpg" alt="e862113444d142df4d9cf8a373fbe464.jpg" width="283" height="215" style="width: 283px; height: 215px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(98, 142, 124); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">教育是一朵云推动另一朵云，一个生命影响另一个生命的过程。师德是为师之范，师风乃立德之基。教师队伍建设好了，才能够培养更加优秀的学生，为祖国输送德才兼备的人才。小到学校的管理，大到落实科教兴国、人才强国战略实现中华民族伟大复兴的高度，筑牢师风师德之基不可或缺。经济管理学院以师德师风为核，落实师德师风建设要求，守望教育初心。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(98, 142, 124); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(247, 253, 255); text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">党总支书记蔡平讲述了几个违反师风师德酿成不可挽回后果的例子，以此突出师风师德建设的迫在眉睫与其重要性。在真实案例中，进一步深化全体教职工对自我师风师德培养的意识。随后，党总支书记蔡平</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">宣读高校教师十项准则。</span></p><p><br/></p>